2000-10-04  Paul D. Smith  <psmith@gnu.org>

	* FvwmForm/FormFvwmRlogin., FvwmForm/FormFvwmForm.: Can't use \n
	in echo commands and expect it to be expanded to a newline
	everywhere: some versions of echo require -e for that to work;
	some versions can't do it at all.  Rewrite the command to avoid
	the need for this.

