	* FvwmButtons/FvwmButtons.c (main):
	* FvwmButtons/parse.c (ParseConfigLine): new option
	*FvwmButtonsButtonGeometry specifies the size of all individual buttons

	* FvwmIconMan/x.c (create_manager_window): IconMan uses resize_inc 1
	vertically too

	* FvwmButtons/button.c (MakeContainer): initialise values with memset

	* FvwmButtons/draw.c (RedrawButton):
	* FvwmButtons/output.c (DumpButtons):
