1999-05-24  Bob Woodside <proteus@pcnet.com>

	* FvwmPager/x_pager.c: Changed to use the new GoToDeskAndPage command.
	This prevents flashing of windows that shouldn't be seen during the
	simultaneous transition to a new desk and page, without the side
	effects of the old "GoToDesk 0 10000" hack.

